titles.title: Providing for an adjournment of the House from Wednesday, November 10, 1993 to Monday, November 15, 1993 and an adjournment or recess of the Senate from Wednesday, November 10, 1993 to Tuesday, November 16, 1993.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

vote.text: Received in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 11/10/1993--Introduced. Provides for an adjournment of the House of Representatives from November 10 until November 15, 1993, and a recess or adjournment of the Senate from November 10 until November 16, 1993.
